---

<footer class={`flex justify-around w-full py-4 ${backgroundColor} ${fixed ? 'fixed' : ''} bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 transition-[background-color] duration-200 ease-in bg-texture bg-4xl sm:bg-xl`}>
	<div class='flex justify-around w-full'>
		<p class='font-bold text-lg'>ARC 2023</p>
		<p>|</p>
		<p class='font-light'>Desarrollado por <a class='underline' target='_blank' href='https://github.com/Strocs'>Strocs</a></p>
	</div>
</footer>
